caller_intent: Ian called to correct an error in an insurance binder for Laura, which was sent with the wrong car model (2024 Camry instead of 2025 RAV4).
resolution_steps: Holly confirmed Brandi was unavailable and took ownership of the request.
Ian provided the policy number (5457476300) and clarified the correct vehicle model needed.
Holly committed to resending the corrected binder immediately.
summary: Ian contacted Alliance Insurance to correct an insurance binder error for Laura's 2025 RAV4, which had been mistakenly issued for a 2024 Camry. Holly resolved the issue by confirming the policy details and committing to send the corrected document.
